spec_data.Name: international-time
spec_data.Description:
This is a graphical tool for converting a local "wall-clock" time into
UTC.  This is useful for arranging conference calls where participants
from other countries are expected
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 05:48:24 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A tool for arranging times in advance with overseas colleagues
